Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻丘歌劇團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像輕音部一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密朱麗演得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戲劇也蠻好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  輕音部也別搞演唱會了  演戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是戲劇部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  是像輕音部一樣的音樂戲劇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（音樂戲劇  純潔之心）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛形成的～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純潔～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之心～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有點難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那換個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（歌劇  咖喱後米飯）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是胡蘿蔔  胡蘿蔔喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋蔥洋蔥洋蔥吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆土豆土～豆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群蔬菜  砍了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嘟咕嘟咕嘟咕嘟  慢慢煮透
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香辣調料  放多多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱哦  咖喱哦  咖喱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這故事都不知道什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:35.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（時代劇  毛筆與圓珠筆）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛筆  FUFU～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（放學後茶會）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和音樂沒關繫了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是表演普通的演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂

